Created by Broadway actress, dancer and celebrity Trainer Amanda Kloots. A 55-minute cardio and toning interval-based workout featuring the AK! Jump Rope. Jump and sculpt using the rope in ways you've never imagined.

71 Classes This Week Enjoy access to 11 class categories, including signature Cycling, high-intensity Boxing and Martial Arts classes, and sculpting Pilates sessions.    All classes in the club and on the Equinox+ app are unlimited and included in your membership.
